<subSubSection box="[199,1203,907,933]" pageId="2" pageNumber="529" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,933]" box="[199,1203,907,933]" pageId="2" pageNumber="529">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,907,933]" pageId="2" pageNumber="529">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after its special abdomen: 
